*IBR Infotech LLP* is a premier technology solutions provider headquartered in Indore, India, with a strategic presence in the USA. With a team of 160+ professionals, they specialize in digital transformation. Tagline: *"Scale Up Your Project In Weeks, And Not Months."*

*Company Overview*
• Website: [www.ibrinfotech.com](https://www.ibrinfotech.com/)

2. *Web Dev:* MERN, Next.js, PHP, Laravel, WordPress

*Industrial Solutions*

*Why Choose Them?*
• Rapid Scaling (weeks, not months)
• 300+ successful projects
• Global Delivery Model
